Day 90: Managing ACLs Using Ansible

Date: December 17, 2025
Overview
Set file system Access Control Lists using Ansible.
Key Concepts Learned

ACL module
Fine-grained permissions
User/group ACLs
Default ACLs

Playbook
yaml- name: Set ACL for user
  acl:
    path: /var/www/html
    entity: webuser
    etype: user
    permissions: rwx
    state: present

Challenges Faced
ACLs are complex! Understanding effective permissions and inheritance.
